  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study aimed to evaluate the effect of cedar honey in treatment of erosive and atrophic
      oral lichen planus ( a common oral problem).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Completed</overall_status>
